The human wants us to form a circle with the center at (150, 100) and a radius of 50. The robots need to be uniformly distributed along the circle. I need to find out how many robots are in the environment and determine my position on the circle. First, I need to know my current position.

```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I have reached the target position (100.2, 100.2), which is close enough to (100, 100). My direction is 138.8 degrees. I think I have completed my task.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
